Class TrainingCentreRetreiveServiceImpl

java.lang.Object
com.org.Traini8.ServiceImplementations.TrainingCentreRetreiveServiceImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
TrainingCenterRetreiveService
@Service public class TrainingCentreRetreiveServiceImpl extends Object implements TrainingCenterRetreiveService
Implementation of TrainingCenterRetreiveService that interacts with the database to fetch and filter data regarding training centers. This service utilizes Spring's Dependency Injection to integrate components and the TrainingCenterRepository for data access operations.

  • Method Details

    • findAllTrainingCenters

      public List<TrainingCentre> findAllTrainingCenters()
      Retrieves all training centers from the database. This method handles any exceptions by logging them and rethrowing as a runtime exception.
      Specified by:
      findAllTrainingCenters in interface TrainingCenterRetreiveService
      Returns:
      a list of all TrainingCentre objects from the database. If no training centers are found, this method returns an empty list.
      Throws:
      RuntimeException - if there is an error during database access.

    • findByMultipleCriteria

      public List<TrainingCentre> findByMultipleCriteria(String centerCode, String centerName, Integer minCapacity, Integer maxCapacity, String contactEmail, String contactPhone, String city, String state, String pincode, List<String> courses)
      Retrieves a list of training centers based on multiple filtering criteria. Parameters are optional and used to filter the results accordingly.
      Specified by:
      findByMultipleCriteria in interface TrainingCenterRetreiveService
      Parameters:
      centerCode - Optional filter by center code.
      centerName - Optional filter by center name.
      minCapacity - Optional filter for minimum capacity.
      maxCapacity - Optional filter for maximum capacity.
      contactEmail - Optional filter by contact email.
      contactPhone - Optional filter by contact phone.
      city - Optional filter by city.
      state - Optional filter by state.
      pincode - Optional filter by pincode.
      courses - Optional list of courses to filter by; centers must offer all listed courses if specified.
      Returns:
      a list of TrainingCentre that meet the specified criteria. If no centers match the criteria, this method returns an empty list.
      Throws:
      RuntimeException - if there is an error during database access or data filtering.
